channel.title: Autocache Downloader Help [PI]
channel.description:
Ive been trying to get my autocache downloader to work for the last like 2 days and nothing seems to work.
What it does is it downloads the cache, then it unzips it, then when it starts to load the cache library and finishes it says "Error loading client - Please report"
So Im not exactly sure whats wrong.
Can anyone help me out with this?
